          "text" : "Discussion",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "This flag aims to reduce unnecessary reconnections while quick app switches,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "like when a user just checks a notification or another app.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "ChatClient",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " starts a background task to keep the connection alive,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "and disconnects when background task expires.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "ChatClient",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " tries to stay connected while in background up to 5 minutes.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Usually, disconnection occurs around 2-3 minutes.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "If youâ€™re using manual connection flow (",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "code" : "shouldConnectAutomatically",
                  "type" : "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " set to ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "code" : "false",
                  "type" : "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "), this flag is ineffective.",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "You should handle connection manually when sending app to background",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "or opening app from background.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "style" : "important",
          "type" : "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Default value is ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "true",
